        "Hip Circles": ExerciseTutorial(images: ["hip_circles"], instructions: "Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, hands on hips. Slowly rotate your hips in a large, smooth circle, pushing them front, side, back, and side.\n\n**Focus:** Lubricating the hip joints."),
