        "Cat-Cow Stretch": ExerciseTutorial(images: [], instructions: "On hands and knees, slowly inhale and drop your belly toward the floor, lifting your chest and tailbone (Cow). Then exhale, round your back toward the ceiling, and tuck your chin (Cat).\n\n**Focus:** Spinal mobility and relieving tension."),
        
