        "Hip Flexor Lunge + Reach": ExerciseTutorial(images: [], instructions: "From a half-kneeling lunge, gently push your hips forward. Raise the arm on the same side as your trailing leg straight up to the ceiling, then lean slightly sideways over the front leg.\n\n**Focus:** Deep hip flexor and psoas stretching."),
